response.original_title: The Rise of Skywalker - A Brief Look At Bad Lore
response.overview: Behold! The sum of our work on the Starwarsification of Disney's The Rise of Skywalker. All five parts, remastered. Over 70 minutes of never before seen material. The first stage in a larger process and a more ambitious goal. Join us for the lore version of the Death Star briefing.  How did Disney go wrong? What does established lore tell us? What are some of the potential fixes?
response.title: The Rise of Skywalker - A Brief Look At Bad Lore
